    <item>
      <title>艾夫斯：马斯克将对白宫产生重大影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/musk-will-have-significant-white-house-influence-ives-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克对唐纳德·特朗普的重注可能会确保他在总统任期内发挥重要作用。韦德布什的丹·艾夫斯与卡罗琳·海德和埃德·卢德洛一起讨论“彭博科技”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/musk-will-have-significant-white-house-influence-ives-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 20:17:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克拉里达：美联储可能明年就结束量化宽松做出决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/fed-decision-on-end-of-qt-could-come-next-year-clarida-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[太平洋投资管理公司 (Pimco) 全球经济顾问、前美联储副主席理查德·克拉里达 (Richard Clarida) 研究了金融状况如何影响美联储的利率路径，并表示在“预算数字相当令人沮丧”的背景下，量化紧缩政策的结束可能是明年的决定。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/fed-decision-on-end-of-qt-could-come-next-year-clarida-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 20:07:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔称通胀已缓解，劳动力市场稳健</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/powell-says-inflation-has-eased-labor-market-is-solid-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，通胀已经缓解，经济活动“继续以稳健的速度扩张”。此前，美联储官员一致投票决定将基准贷款利率下调四分之一个百分点。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/powell-says-inflation-has-eased-labor-market-is-solid-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 20:05:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lightspeed 继续进行战略评估，寻求提高效率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/lightspeed-looks-for-efficiencies-as-strategic-review-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大支付公司 Lightspeed Commerce Inc. 股价周四上涨 13%，此前该公司公布了可能导致出售的战略评估和更好的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/lightspeed-looks-for-efficiencies-as-strategic-review-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 19:40:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通的米歇尔：一直在市场上购买债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/jpmorgan-s-michele-been-in-the-market-buying-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通资产管理公司固定收益全球主管 Bob Michele 解释了该公司为何一直在购买债券，并表示公司债券市场“看起来比长期美国国债更具吸引力”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/jpmorgan-s-michele-been-in-the-market-buying-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 19:23:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储将利率下调四分之一个百分点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/federal-reserve-cuts-interest-rates-by-a-quarter-point-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储将基准贷款利率下调四分之一个百分点至 4.5% 至 4.75% 之间。投票结果一致通过。彭博社的 Michael McKee 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/federal-reserve-cuts-interest-rates-by-a-quarter-point-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 19:21:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行总裁罗伯茨表示，这是数周以来第一轮裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/hsbc-s-roberts-says-first-round-of-job-losses-in-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行新成立的全球批发银行部门主管表示，该行将寻求“迅速”完成正在进行的重组，并可能在几周内宣布第一轮裁员。迈克尔·罗伯茨 (Michael Roberts) 接受彭博社 Manus Cranny 采访时谈到了该行的重组。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/hsbc-s-roberts-says-first-round-of-job-losses-in-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 19:10:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日产汽车下调业绩预期，宣布重组并裁员 9,000 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/nissan-cuts-outlook-announces-restructing-with-9-000-job-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日产汽车公司在应对汽车行业日益严峻的形势和解决内部弱点方面遇到的困难不断加剧，迫使该公司不得不削减工资、产量并降低本财年的业绩预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/nissan-cuts-outlook-announces-restructing-with-9-000-job-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 07:53:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普上台后，油价上涨，交易员分析产量和地缘政治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们正在消化关于唐纳德·特朗普担任总统将如何影响原油市场的各种相互矛盾的说法，油价跟随股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:28:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔给出“无跳过迹象” 股市接近高点：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市创下历史新高，美国国债收益率下跌，美元创下自 8 月以来的最大跌幅，杰罗姆鲍威尔表示，即使在周四降息后，政策仍然具有限制性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:21:50 GMT</pubDate>
